responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "632ECC2A46517B23B0E7AF85A976B5B6", "Right, let\'s get on with it then? The bulk of the scroll is certainly Goblish, though it appears to be a letter written by someone that\'s not a goblin. Goblins aren\'t articulate enough to use a quill such as this, so this was clearly someone much more refined. The quality of the parchment is exquisite, so I surmise that the author is likely of great wealth or prestige, perhaps. Though the seal adorned upon this isn\'t of anything in our academy archives.")
